				<td colspan="2"><span>Just to add my comments here, when I tried this, quite often mobs would hit me a fair bit which really, really hurt.
<br />
Then I found a neat little trick that helped me for quite a few levels;
<br />
I'd keep running while I was casting Charm
<br />
Once I did this, I managed to stay ahead of the mobs and get something charmed without being hit.  Sometimes, if my concentration was really good, I'd be able to get Selo's working too, and this REALLY helped me keep ahead of the mobs, though the speed sometimes made me a bit dizzy, especially after running in circles for a bit, so I'd have to log off, lie down for a few minutes before coming back to kill another mob.  
<br />
Really AWSOME xp though, I'd recommend anyone to try it.
