				<td colspan="2"><span>While we're talking about secret methods of getting good exp.  Try this one.  Find one of the zones that gives you good exp when you chant kite stuff down.  Now, get another person who plays a warrior, and a person who plays a cleric.  If you want, find some more people who will do fast damage.  Now, target each one of them individually and type &quot;/invite&quot;.  Once they all type the same, then go out and get a monster.  I call this &quot;pulling&quot;.  When you &quot;pull&quot; the monster to your friends (I call them a &quot;group&quot; ) they all gang up on it and kill it.  You'd be amazed how fast things die this way.  I first started doing this when LDoN came out, and I think I'm pretty much the only one who knows about it.  Maybe it's not for everybody though.</span></td>
