				<td colspan="2"><span>Yeah so this is probably the last time I start a thread.  You guys who were bashing me, go choke on some sausage. 
<br />

<br />
I posted this because I figured out how to do it on my own and never had heard anyone else talk about it and I don't go to forums ofter, I just play the game.  When hanging with my friend the other night (level 64 bard)  I told him about it and he said he had never heard about it and that I should post what I do to get soloing exp.  So I did.  Sorry I didn't get the right &quot;term&quot; for it, like I said I figured out how to do it on my own.  Should get props right there.  I don't need to read a forum to figure out how to play my class.
<br />

<br />
I found out that invis works fine to release charmed pet.  I had heard a rumor that it didn't.
<br />

<br />
Oh and about being one of the first to lvl 65 on my server, that's true.  I went to PoD and swarm kited in the swampy area with flies, then moved to PoN and did warewolfs until level 64 then did the goblins and nightmares till 65 and got like 17aa there too.  It really works pretty well.
<br />

<br />
Thanks to all the guys who weren't pole smokers in this thread.</span></td>
